ise awareness of harassment.\n\nThe film you are about to see is fiction that may offend the sensibilities of some people.\nIf you wish, you can remove your headset at any time."}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "957618459482056", "locale": "fr_FR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Heureusement que tu \u00e9tais l\u00e0 !", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Une suite de vid\u00e9os 360\u00b0 dont le sc\u00e9nario d\u00e9pend de vos choix.\nLors d'une soir\u00e9e \u00e9tudiante, vous \u00eates t\u00e9moin d'une forme de harc\u00e8lement. C'est \u00e0 vous de choisir comment r\u00e9agir.\n\nLe film que vous allez voir est une fiction pouvant heurter la sensibilit\u00e9 de certaines personnes.\nSi vous le souhaitez, vous pouvez retirer votre casque \u00e0 tout moment.", "short_description": "Vid\u00e9os 360\u00b0 interactive pour sensibiliser au harc\u00e8lement.\n\nLe film que vous allez voir est une fiction pouvant heurter la sensibilit\u00e9 de certaines personnes.\nSi vous le souhaitez, vous pouvez retirer votre casque \u00e0 tout moment."}]}, "developer_name": "iCAP - Universit\u00e9 Lyon 1", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://virtuallab.univ-lyon1.fr/privacy-policy-for-heureusement-que-tu-etais-la/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "iCAP - Universit\u00e9 Lyon 1", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://virtuallab.univ-lyon1.fr/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2837265163266059", "context_category": "ENTERTAINMENT"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1283811691952063"}, {"id": "879473995923081"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["fr"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCU